  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">In addition we disclose certain personal information to the issuer of the MasterCard in connection with the administration of the Barnes Noble MasterCard program The issuer does not have the right to use the personal information we provide beyond what is necessary to assist us or to administer this program The issuer is contractually obliged to maintain the confidentiality and security of the personal information we provide and is restricted from using such information in any way not expressly authorized by us</evidence>
